    if not lst1 or not lst2:
        return None
    result = []
    max_val1 = max(lst1)
    min_val1 = min(lst1)
    max_val2 = max(lst2)
    min_val2 = min(lst2)
    result.append(max_val1 - min_val1)
    result.append(max_val2 - min_val2)
    return result
